name: Gully Cricket
description: Effervescence'17 presents to you the most entertaining event "GULLY CRICKET". Make your Team of Bluster and Come to play game of spirit. Win Cash and other exciting prizes...

name: Perplexus
description: An online treasure hunt competition for the ecth geeks who would like to keep it simple yet competitive!

name: Stegolica
description: A delight for all the aspiring hackers and crackers , Stegolica is an online cryptography competition which has one of the most toughest competitors trying to prove themselves.

name: Futsal
description: Test your real life football skills and motor skill-mojo in this five-a-side, small area, short time version of football. Viva la futsal!

name: Blind Date
description: Let the cupid strike your heart, have a date to spend some time with and then well, who knows what can happen!

name: Night on Boards
description: This is event is for all the board game nerds, held at night for your convenience. Effervescence never sleeps and better even, never stops playing. Sounds perfect, no?

name: China Town
description: Effervescence'17  presents you China Town, an event filled with card games like Poker, Teen Patti and Darts. Come and witness your dream turn into reality.

name: Tug-of-War
description: Effervescence'17 present to you the "Tug-of-War" that tests your strength and character.

name: Just A Minute
description: Amazing hand-eye coordination, sharp and fast thinking, and a zest to win are prerequisites for this reboot of A Minute to Win It.

name: AdMania
description: Ever saw an advertisement and thought you could do sometime a lot better? Well here is your chance.

name: Counter Strike Global Offensive
description: For the hardcore gamers, we bring to your service the game of the generation - Counter Strike. Happy Hunting!!

name: Fifa17
description: FIFA is an online football gaming event played with La Liga format where the winning teams will be decided according to a  knockout round.

name: Android Gamer�s Asylum
description: This event consists of a competition of popular Android Games like Mini Militia, Bomb Squad.

name: Paanipuri Junction
description: Panipuri Junction gives you an opportunity to show your love for the food with the simplest of competitions. Eat as many golgappas as you want in a minute without having to pay for it and may be win something out of it.

name: TV Series Quiz
description: From Game Of Thrones to Suits and From How I Met Your Mother to Friends, this event will make you relive those amazing moments to the core.

name: Cricket Quiz
description: Who was the first person to score 300 runs in a test match? If you�ve got the answers, we�ve got the competition and some really tough questions coming your way in this three-round quiz.

name: Animania
description: Think you're the biggest anime freak out there? Come , participate and meet your kind(of people).

name: Roadies
description: If you've got the brains and the brawn, look no further for the ultimate test of your physical and mental strength. This is no mere reboot of the T.V. series.

name: Photobooth
description: If you are obsessed with getting yourself clicked, then we present the Photo Booth for you where you can have your pictures taken with props and all the dreamworks of a carnival presented just for you! Enter Pose and Click!

name: Arm Wrestling
description: Come show where the hours you put into the gym and the push-ups and chin-ups you do have taken you in the competition where the strongest prevails!!

name: Basketball
description: An informal basketball sporting event with custom rules made for you!!

name: Treasure Hunt
description: "The treasure awaits you only if you search for it."The Treasure Hunt ensures that you enjoy running around the college in search of clues. Wherever the clues will be you will search them, find them and open the way to the final treasure.

name: La Frenze
description: One of the most electrifying and enthralling dance events of Effervescence organized by the Dance society, this is a duet dance event.

name: Carpe Diem
description: Because dancing requires great passion and not great skills. It is a solo dance competition.

name: Show off
description: "Show Off" is an online dance competition.

name: Bindass Bol (Nukkad Natak)
description: It is one of the art of drama through which you convey your thoughts or do satire on the social activities which are wrong but still happening in our society.

name: Director's Cut
description: An online short film making competition on a theme.

name: Tongues On Fire
description: It is a fun event organized by the Dramatics Society where teams debate over common topics.

name: Double Trouble
description: Another fun event of the Dramatics Society in which small tasks are given to the participants and points are awarded.

name: Kahani
description: An online event to test your writing skills.

name: Antakshari
description: As soon as you read the word Antakshari, you grew nostalgic ,didn�t you? This event holds an appeal for all be it the old school melody lovers or the modern pop culture enthusiasts.

name: Unplugged
description: Introducing Unplugged,the official acoustic event organised during Effervescence. We invite you to this musical event where you can perform acoustic renditions of your favourite songs and win attractive prizes.

name: Psychedelia
description: Psychedellia is the mainstage non-competitive event for Musical Bands, with no judges. Being a mainstage event of Effervescence, it presents you with an opportunity that will always be a win win situation.

name: Melodeiux
description: Melodieux is a competitive music event organised for just singers. May the one with the best voice win!

name: Feathers
description: "Feathers", is the annual creative writing event conducted during Effervescence.

name: Cognoscentia
description: Congnoscentia is organised each year to put your grey cells into work. This mind numbing quizzing competition covers every genre, Literally, everything under the sun!

name: Dumb Charades
description: Get geared up for the game of phrases represented in pantomime as we present to you, a cherished and allured pastime-it�s all about dumb charades.

name: One on One
description: 'One on One� brings with it, a platform to enhance your talking and debating skills.

name: Meme Slam
description: Meme Slam, is the launchpad for people with a good sensse of humour who can put their cool ideas on posts(not paper!)..

name: Sketcher
description: Sketcher is an online sketching competition for all the art lovers out there. You just have to take a pencil or a pen or pencil colours and shape your imagination on the paper.

name: Face Painting
description: Face painting is an event where one participant showcase his talent by painting the face of his teammate based on the theme given on the spot.

name: Graffiti
description: Do you feel that that drawing sheet is too small to showcase your imagination? Graffiti is the best place for you in such a case!

name: Toon Coon
description: Toon Coon is where you can make a cartoon based on the themes which will be provided to you on the spot.

name: Tasveer
description: Explore the hidden photographer in you with the event TASVEER. Just take your camera and click, not when it seems like, but when it feels like.

name: Mannequin Challenge
description: A great gang, a pinch of creativity, a recorder and that's all the ingredients required to fetch you cool prizes. So just play with your camera, juggle your mind and come with the most boggling mannequin.

name: Safar
description: College is that time of life when people make the best memories when they think they're having fun. To capture these memories and have them stored for you all long your life, we present to you, SAFAR, an online photography event that expands its boundaries beyond conventional photography contests.

name: Footloose
description: Groovy beats and Dancing. The main stagedance event at Effervescence promises the outpour of the hearts desires with the beats of music.
location: Main Stage set inside the campus.

name: Innovation
description: All emotions come at play with a plethora of feelings at the main stage event for Dramatics. A chance not only to showcase one's talent but also to take home a handsome cash prize.

name: Incendiary
description: College Bands battling for recognition and the thrill to perform in front of a live audience. Great competition, Greater effort.

name: EDM Night
description: The rage of today-128 BPM big room rage stuff from the likes of Tieso, Hardwell, Martin Garrix and so on. Performed under SunBurn by renowned artist such as AceAxe, SickLead and more in the past, guess what lies ahead!

name: Humour Night
description: Make your days less gloomy and your life a little happier. Come join us this autumn where we introduce the Humour Night.

name: Bollywood Night
description: Bollywood is a religion and the devotees are plenty. Get ready for whats in store this year as the legacy from Daler Mehandi, Sona Mahapatra, Neha Kakkar to Benny Dayal follows.

name: Headliner
description: The standard has been set high with The Local Train performing in the previous edition and bigger and better can surely be expected in this edition.

name: A'La Mode
description: High on the Fashion quotient and too Glam to give a Damn, the Fashionistas eccentricate the stage in all colours and outfits in the Fashion Show at Effervescence'17.
